<br>
The bottom line is that I spent most of a perfectly good day, no make that damn beautiful day, cooped up in the house not doing anything constructive playing EQ and not having anything to show for it.<br>
<br>
I'm not feeling very happy right now.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START >: --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/mad.gif ALT=">:"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Coddington<br>
<br>
